All fixes verified. Here's a summary of what was found and corrected:

---

**Populate_P6_Variance_Annual_From_Spread.sql — 2 fixes:**

| Issue | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| CPDid separators | `ProjectID\|ActivityID\|ResourceID\|CostElementID\|Year` | `ZFILL(ProjectID,4) + ActivityID + ResourceID + CostElementID + Year` (no separators) |
| CPDid ProjectID padding | `"21"` | `"0021"` via `RIGHT('0000' + ProjectID, 4)` |
| CostElementID trailing space | `LEFT(CostElement, pos-1)` → `"611100 "` | `RTRIM(LEFT(...))` → `"611100"` |
| GROUP BY CPDid | CPDid was in GROUP BY (can cause wrong grouping) | Removed — CPDid is now computed from grain columns in SELECT |

