EXEC dbo.Run_PJC_Append_P6_Annuals_Full SYSDATETIME(), 500000.0;
```

- Use GETDATE() if you prefer:
```sql
EXEC dbo.Run_PJC_Append_P6_Annuals_Full @DateStamp = GETDATE(), @Threshold = 500000.0;
```

Or omit @DateStamp to let the procedure default:
